Synopsis:
This is the main hag dialogue. In it, you can ask about Mayrina (who is present) or make a deal to have your parasite removed. 

If you keep asking about Mayrina (twice), the hag will be furious and vanish Mayrina away while she deals with the 'busybody' - the player.

If you agree to the tadpole deal, you must give up an eye (in the transformed dialogue).
